    <text>
        <body>

        <p><span facs="#zone_5a0fae2e-c398-11e8-892f-f40f243b5e05">|</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fb0e8-c398-11e8-b871-f40f243b5e05">|</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fb27a-c398-11e8-b149-f40f243b5e05">|</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fb3da-c398-11e8-a9ca-f40f243b5e05">|</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fb522-c398-11e8-ba93-f40f243b5e05">|</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fb662-c398-11e8-a5b3-f40f243b5e05">謹啓</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fb7ac-c398-11e8-a514-f40f243b5e05">春風略湯の候読々御多祥奉項候</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fb8e2-c398-11e8-8c4d-f40f243b5e05">陳者山4係致居候第一ホテルの儀北程建築共子を淡へ</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fba2c-c398-11e8-98d2-f40f243b5e05">急々来る四月九日開業の運びと相成候に就ては何卒特別</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fbb62-c398-11e8-b627-f40f243b5e05">の御庇護を賜はり度伏して奉懇願候</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fbc98-c398-11e8-b053-f40f243b5e05">」</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fbdda-c398-11e8-b154-f40f243b5e05">営ホテルの特長としては別紙御案内書の如く共建築は近代</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fbf10-c398-11e8-b25b-f40f243b5e05">科導の粋を集め全館暖房冷房装置は勿論持に防音に留意仕</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fc046-c398-11e8-b5be-f40f243b5e05">候而して共位置は新橋銀座に隣接致し帝國議事堂其他</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fc17a-c398-11e8-8ece-f40f243b5e05">諸官商並に商業中心地たる丸の内方面も精呼の間に有之候</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fc2b0-c398-11e8-ace5-f40f243b5e05">室数六百五拾華麗を極めたる大社交室大小食を始めグリ</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fc3f0-c398-11e8-a54b-f40f243b5e05">ル等の設け有之総て現代一流ホテルに比も卵も色なく質</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fc530-c398-11e8-b23d-f40f243b5e05">に東洋最大最高を誇るものとして御満足の御業賜はる事</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fc66e-c398-11e8-8b69-f40f243b5e05">と確信致居候丈特に留意仕候は</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fc7b0-c398-11e8-862a-f40f243b5e05">てに次て冗費を省き御負</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fc8e6-c398-11e8-9281-f40f243b5e05">塔の軽減を計り現代一流ホテルに比し四</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fca1c-c398-11e8-80f7-f40f243b5e05">・</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fcb5c-c398-11e8-b2dd-f40f243b5e05">五割か低廉と相</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fcc92-c398-11e8-90b4-f40f243b5e05">2662345533333355333803</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fcdc8-c398-11e8-994d-f40f243b5e05">|</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fcf08-c398-11e8-887b-f40f243b5e05">|</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fd048-c398-11e8-b7d1-f40f243b5e05">|</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fd17e-c398-11e8-9966-f40f243b5e05">|</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fd2c0-c398-11e8-9784-f40f243b5e05">|</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fd3f6-c398-11e8-92b8-f40f243b5e05">成る次第に御座候料理に就而も優秀なる一流調理人を集め</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fd536-c398-11e8-aaa4-f40f243b5e05">各位の御賞讃を博し得る事と存候</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fd66c-c398-11e8-ac56-f40f243b5e05">前述の次第に御座候へば</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fd7a2-c398-11e8-81d5-f40f243b5e05">御逗留は勿論大小御無織等には足</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fd8de-c398-11e8-a60e-f40f243b5e05">非御利用被成下丈御動カ下の方々へも御吹敷被下様切に御</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fda18-c398-11e8-b462-f40f243b5e05">依頼中上度先は御披露愛く御願之如斯御座候</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fdb4c-c398-11e8-a2d9-f40f243b5e05">具</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fdc82-c398-11e8-bdc1-f40f243b5e05">8</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fddc0-c398-11e8-860b-f40f243b5e05">月</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fdef8-c398-11e8-8147-f40f243b5e05">日</span><span facs="#zone_5a0fe038-c398-11e8-a5c7-f40f243b5e05">みえこ</span></p></body>
